                  </hi>. I keep a shop in Leather-lane. On Saturday night, 12th Oct., as I was taking in my goods, I saw the prisoner take a pair of boots off the rail outside my window—he ran away; I ran after</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185010210110"></xptr>
               <p>him—I only lost sight of him as he turned the corner—I came nearly up to him, but did not catch him—these are my boots (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>).</p>
